<br>
Worse though is that there really isn't anything to do other than raid anymore.  That's the entire high-end game, raid, raid raid.  Raid and raid some more.  Then we'll add flags to some of these raid mobs and make them spawn every three days.  The guild that can log in earliest with 50+ people gets to play God and control these spawns until they see fit to allow someone else to progress.  <br>
<br>
They wonder why EQ is suffering?  It's because EQ is nothing but raiding and raiding has never given the player base a fair shake.<br>
